vote.title: Authorize an amendment to an existing license agreement with AIDS Arms, Inc., to extend the license agreement for an additional five-years for approximately 19,876 square feet of City-owned land located at 210 Sunset Avenue for the continued, non-exclusive use of 30 parking spaces for employees, guests and clients for the period December 15, 2020 through December 14, 2025 - Revenue: General Fund $43,680.00
